type\": \"module\",\n  \"engines\": { \"node\": \">=18\" },\n  \"packageManager\": \"pnpm@10.30.3\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"pnpm -r --filter='./packages/*' run build\",\n    \"typecheck\": \"tsc --noEmit\",\n    \"dev\": \"pnpm --filter playground run dev\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@types/node\": \"^22.0.0\",\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.7.0\",\n    \"vue\": \"^3.5.0\",\n    \"vite\": \"^6.0.0\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**`/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/pnpm-workspace.yaml`**\n```yaml\npackages:\n  - 'packages/*'\n  - 'playground'\n```\n\n**`/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/tsconfig.base.json`**\n```json\n{\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"target\": \"ES2022\",\n    \"module\": \"ESNext\",\n    \"moduleResolution\": \"bundler\",\n    \"strict\": true,\n    \"esModuleInterop\": true,\n    \"skipLibCheck\": true,\n    \"forceConsistentCasingInFileNames\": true,\n    \"resolveJsonModule\": true,\n    \"isolatedModules\": true,\n    \"declaration\": true,\n    \"sourceMap\": true,\n    \"baseUrl\": \".\",\n    \"paths\": {\n      \"@vuepoint/core\": [\"./packages/core/src/index.ts\"],\n      \"@vuepoint/vue\": [\"./packages/vue/src/index.ts\"],\n      \"@vuepoint/bridge\": [\"./packages/bridge/src/index.ts\"]\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. PACKAGE: @vuepoint/core\n\n**Location:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/core`\n\n**`package.json`**\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"@vuepoint/core\",\n  \"version\": \"0.1.0\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"exports\": {\n    \".\": {\n      \"import\": \"./dist/index.js\",\n      \"require\": \"./dist/index.cjs\",\n      \"types\": \"./dist/index.d.ts\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"main\": \"./dist/index.cjs\",\n  \"module\": \"./dist/index.js\",\n  \"types\": \"./dist/index.d.ts\",\n  \"files\": [\"dist\"],\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"echo 'build configured in US-002'\",\n    \"typecheck\": \"tsc --noEmit\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.7.0\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**`tsconfig.json`**\n```json\n{\n  \"extends\": \"../../tsconfig.base.json\",\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"outDir\": \"dist\",\n    \"rootDir\": \"src\"\n  },\n  \"include\": [\"src\"]\n}\n```\n\n**Source Files:**\n- `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/core/src/index.ts` - Main exports\n- `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/core/src/types.ts` - Core type definitions (AnnotationStatus, Annotation, WebhookPayload, VuePointOptions, etc.)\n- `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/core/src/selector.ts` - CSS selector generation utilities\n- `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/core/src/output.ts` - Markdown formatting and output utilities\n- `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/core/src/primevue-filter.ts` - PrimeVue component filtering\n\n---\n\n### 3. PACKAGE: @vuepoint/vue\n\n**Location:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue`\n\n**`package.json`**\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"@vuepoint/vue\",\n  \"version\": \"0.1.0\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"exports\": {\n    \".\": {\n      \"import\": \"./dist/index.js\",\n      \"require\": \"./dist/index.cjs\",\n      \"types\": \"./dist/index.d.ts\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"main\": \"./dist/index.cjs\",\n  \"module\": \"./dist/index.js\",\n  \"types\": \"./dist/index.d.ts\",\n  \"files\": [\"dist\"],\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"echo 'build configured in US-002'\",\n    \"typecheck\": \"tsc --noEmit\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@vuepoint/core\": \"workspace:*\"\n  },\n  \"peerDependencies\": {\n    \"vue\": \"^3.4.0\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"vue\": \"^3.5.0\",\n    \"vite\": \"^6.0.0\",\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.7.0\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**`tsconfig.json`**\n```json\n{\n  \"extends\": \"../../tsconfig.base.json\",\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"outDir\": \"dist\",\n    \"rootDir\": \"src\",\n    \"jsx\": \"preserve\"\n  },\n  \"include\": [\"src/**/*.ts\", \"src/**/*.d.ts\", \"src/**/*.vue\"]\n}\n```\n\n**Source Files:**\n- `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue