t_annotations` - Fetch annotations (filterable by status)\n    - `vuepoint_get_annotation` - Get single annotation by ID\n    - `vuepoint_acknowledge` - Mark annotation as acknowledged\n    - `vuepoint_resolve` - Mark as resolved with optional summary\n    - `vuepoint_dismiss` - Mark as dismissed with reason\n    - `vuepoint_ask` - Send clarifying questions back to annotator\n    - `vuepoint_get_component_info` - Query Vue component metadata by selector/name\n    - `vuepoint_get_app_context` - Get current route, page component, active stores\n  - **Bridge Communication:** HTTP bridge to SharedWorker on port 3741 (default)\n\n---\n\n### 5. PACKAGE: @vuepoint/api\n\n**Location:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/api`\n\n**`package.json`**\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"@vuepoint/api\",\n  \"version\": \"0.1.0\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"bin\": {\n    \"vuepoint-api\": \"./dist/api.js\"\n  },\n  \"exports\": {\n    \".\": {\n      \"import\": \"./dist/api.js\",\n      \"types\": \"./dist/api.d.ts\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"files\": [\"dist\"],\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"echo 'build configured in US-002'\",\n    \"typecheck\": \"tsc --noEmit\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@vuepoint/core\": \"workspace:*\",\n    \"fastify\": \"^5.2.0\",\n    \"@fastify/cors\": \"^11.0.0\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.7.0\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**`tsconfig.json`**\n```json\n{\n  \"extends\": \"../../tsconfig.base.json\",\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"outDir\": \"dist\",\n    \"rootDir\": \"src\"\n  },\n  \"include\": [\"src\"]\n}\n```\n\n**Source Files:**\n- `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/api/src/api.ts` - REST API + Webhook bridge server (Fastify-based)\n  - **Dual Roles:**\n    1. REST API for external tooling/dashboards (port 3742 default)\n    2. HTTP bridge for browser SharedWorker вҶ” MCP server communication (port 3741 default)\n  - **Endpoints:**\n    - `/health` - Health check\n    - `/api/v1/annotations` - CRUD operations (GET, POST, PATCH, DELETE)\n    - `/api/v1/annotations/export` - Export (JSON or Markdown format)\n    - `/api/v1/annotations/:id` - Get/update/delete single annotation\n    - `/api/v1/annotations/:id/ask` - Send questions to annotator\n    - `/api/v1/context` - Sync/get app context (route, component, stores)\n    - `/api/v1/component` - Component inspection (by selector or name)\n    - `/api/v1/webhooks` - Webhook management and testing\n  - **Features:**\n    - In-memory annotation store (replaceable with SQLite/Redis)\n    - Webhook engine with retry logic (3 attempts with backoff)\n    - Auth token support\n    - CORS configuration\n\n---\n\n### 6. PACKAGE: @vuepoint/bridge\n\n**Location:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/bridge`\n\n**`package.json`**\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"@vuepoint/bridge\",\n  \"version\": \"0.1.0\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"private\": true,\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"echo 'bridge build configured in US-023'\",\n    \"typecheck\": \"tsc --noEmit\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@vuepoint/core\": \"workspace:*\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.7.0\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**`tsconfig.json`**\n```json\n{\n  \"extends\": \"../../tsconfig.base.json\",\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"outDir\": \"dist\",\n    \"rootDir\": \"src\"\n  },\n  \"include\": [\"src\"]\n}\n```\n\n**Source Files:**\n- `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/bridge/src/index.ts` - Placeholder for SharedWorker implementation (US-023)\n  - **Status:** Not yet implemented - noted as \"TODO\" in placeholder\n\n---\n\n### 7. PACKAGE: @jumpcloud/nuxt-vuepoint\n\n**Location:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/nuxt`\n\n**`package.json`**\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"@jumpcloud/nuxt-vuepoint\",\n  \"version\": \"0.1.0\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"private\": true,\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"echo 'nuxt module configured in US-029'\",\n    \"typecheck\": \"tsc --noEmit\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n  