l.vue\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ       в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ AnnotationMarker.vue\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ composables/\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ           в”ңв”Җв”Җ useAnnotations.ts\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ           в””в”Җв”Җ useVueInspector.ts\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ mcp/                     (MCP server for Claude/agents)\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ package.json\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ tsconfig.json\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ src/\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ server.ts\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ api/                     (REST API + webhook bridge)\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ package.json\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ tsconfig.json\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ src/\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ api.ts\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ bridge/                  (SharedWorker - TODO: US-023)\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ package.json\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ tsconfig.json\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ src/\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ index.ts\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ nuxt/                    (Nuxt integration - TODO: US-029)\nв”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ package.json\nв”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ tsconfig.json\nв”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ src/\nв”Ӯ           в””в”Җв”Җ index.ts\nв”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җ playground/                  (Dev environment - TODO: US-014)\n    в””в”Җв”Җ package.json\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. KEY ARCHITECTURAL NOTES\n\n**Communication Flow:**\n1. **Browser вҶ’ API**: Vue plugin sends annotations via HTTP to API\n2. **MCP Server вҶ” API**: MCP server bridges via HTTP to API on port 3741\n3. **Webhooks**: API fires outbound webhooks for annotation events\n4. **Component Hierarchy**: Vue plugin captures full component chain without PrimeVue internals\n\n**No Vite.config files** exist at the root or package level - configuration will need to be added.\n\n**All packages are ES modules** (`\"type\": \"module\"`) with TypeScript support.\n\n**Placeholder implementations** marked in config files for three features:\n- Bridge/SharedWorker (US-023)\n- Nuxt module (US-029)\n- Playground dev (US-014)\n\nThis is a comprehensive, modular monorepo structure ready for build and integration wo