{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Xu5w66Dc59aXH9QdpY1b2H","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`вҳ… Insight в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`\n**DTS and Cross-Package References**: When `vite-plugin-dts` generates declarations for `@vuepoint/vue`, it follows `@vuepoint/core` imports through the `paths` mapping in `tsconfig.base.json`, hitting `rootDir` violations. The fix is a separate `tsconfig.build.json` with empty `paths: {}` вҖ” this tells DTS to treat `@vuepoint/core` as an opaque external package (using its published `.d.ts` rather than source). The dev `tsconfig.json` still uses paths for IDE resolution.\n`в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`\n\nNow let's rebuild:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":513,"cache_read_input_tokens":81380,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":513},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"04004700-d8fd-4b80-9310-fd2da006cc99","uuid":"843083dc-22ea-44df-8334-75510b17e397"}
