{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01WgkiRgp1iX6AdCoqRJi7bc","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"US-002 is complete. There are still many stories with `passes: false` remaining.\n\n`вҳ… Insight в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`\n**Vite Library Mode Strategy for Monorepos**: The key architectural choices here were:\n1. **Library packages** (core, vue) use `formats: ['es', 'cjs']` for maximum consumer compatibility, with `vite-plugin-dts` bundling declarations into a single `.d.ts`\n2. **CLI packages** (mcp, api) use `formats: ['es']` only вҖ” they're runnable entry points, not libraries, and both use top-level `await` which requires ESM\n3. **External dependencies** are carefully listed per-package: runtime deps (`fastify`, `zod`) are externalized while internal code is bundled, keeping the output lean\n`в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`\n\n**Summary**: US-002 is implemented and committed. All 4 publishable packages now build via Vite with correct output formats. `pnpm build` and `pnpm typecheck` both pass clean."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":184,"cache_read_input_tokens":91804,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":184},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"04004700-d8fd-4b80-9310-fd2da006cc99","uuid":"e69bde23-2e74-4e13-8127-bc4f00064285"}
