{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_012nDLLEmZ53crYcp8NzXvda","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All acceptance criteria verified:\n\n1. **`formatAnnotation()`** outputs Markdown with Element, Selector, Component chain, SFC Path, Pinia Stores, Feedback, Expected, Actual, Route вҖ” all present at lines 25-71\n2. **`formatAnnotationBatch()`** formats multiple annotations with headers (`### Annotation [id]`) and `---` separators вҖ” lines 85-107\n3. **Optional fields omitted when empty** вҖ” `expected`, `actual`, `piniaStores` all guarded by conditionals (lines 42-44, 64-71)\n4. **Output is greppable/machine-parseable** вҖ” uses `**Key:** \\`value\\`` format throughout\n5. **Typecheck passes** вҖ” confirmed clean\n\nNow let me commit and update the PRD."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":424,"cache_read_input_tokens":61137,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":424},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f0808652-e48a-417f-9c20-e2d9d25dbac2","uuid":"ae14153a-c202-45fb-80d5-877ff821b060"}
