{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01SuF3tNdQRSsVEjZowuUiJ1","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me provide you with a comprehensive report of all annotation state management files:\n\n## Annotation State Management Files Report\n\nI found **7 key files** related to annotation state management in the VuePoint monorepo:\n\n### **packages/vue/src/composables/useAnnotations.ts**\n**Absolute Path:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue/src/composables/useAnnotations.ts`\n\n**Summary:** The core annotation state management composable. This is the single source of truth for all annotations in the current session. It's a Vue 3 composition API function that manages reactive annotation state without using Pinia (intentionally isolated). Provides:\n- **State:** `annotations` (readonly), `pending` (computed filter)\n- **Reads:** `getById(id)`\n- **Writes (CRUD):** `create()`, `update()`, `acknowledge()`, `resolve()`, `dismiss()`, `remove()`, `clear()`\n- Exports `AnnotationsStore` type and `VUEPOINT_ANNOTATIONS_KEY` Symbol for inject/provide\n\n---\n\n### **packages/core/src/types.ts**\n**Absolute Path:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/core/src/types.ts`\n\n**Summary:** TypeScript type definitions for the annotation system:\n- `AnnotationStatus` type: 'pending' | 'acknowledged' | 'resolved' | 'dismissed'\n- `Annotation` interface: Full annotation object with selector, elementDescription, componentChain, feedback, expected/actual fields, timestamps, and status tracking fields\n- `AnnotationCreateInput` type: Input shape for creating annotations\n- `VueComponentInfo` interface: Component metadata (name, file path, line number, props)\n- `AnnotationRect` interface: Position/scroll data for annotation markers\n- `WebhookEvent` and `WebhookPayload` types for event notifications\n- `VuePointOptions` configuration type\n\n---\n\n### **packages/vue/src/plugin.ts**\n**Absolute Path:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue/src/plugin.ts`\n\n**Summary:** The main Vue 3 plugin that integrates annotation management:\n- Initializes `useAnnotationsStore()` composable\n- Provides annotation store to the entire app via `app.provide(VUEPOINT_ANNOTATIONS_KEY, annotationsStore)`\n- Creates an isolated Vue app instance for the VuePoint toolbar (prevents component chain pollution)\n- Registers keyboard shortcut (default: ctrl+shift+a) to toggle the toolbar\n- Guards against production builds (auto-disables if not in dev/staging)\n- Passes options and built component filters to toolbar\n\n---\n\n### **packages/core/src/output.ts**\n**Absolute Path:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/core/src/output.ts`\n\n**Summary:** Utilities for formatting annotations:\n- `formatAnnotation(ann, opts)`: Formats a single annotation as Markdown with selector, component chain, SFC path, Pinia stores, route, props, feedback, expected/actual\n- `formatAnnotationBatch(annotations, opts)`: Formats all pending annotations as a batch Markdown document\n- `generateId()`: Creates unique annotation IDs using timestamp + random string\n- `now()`: Returns current ISO timestamp\n\n---\n\n### **packages/vue/src/components/AnnotationPanel.vue**\n**Absolute Path:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue/src/components/AnnotationPanel.vue`\n\n**Summary:** UI component stub (Phase 2 - US-011). Currently a placeholder that:\n- Accepts `store: AnnotationsStore` prop\n- Emits `close` event\n- Will display scrollable list of all annotations in the full implementation\n\n---\n\n### **packages/vue/src/components/AnnotationMarker.vue**\n**Absolute Path:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue/src/components/AnnotationMarker.vue`\n\n**Summary:** UI component stub (Phase 2 - US-010). Currently a placeholder that:\n- Accepts `annotation: Annotation` and `index: number` props\n- Displays numbered badge for each annotation\n- Will be positioned overlay markers on annotated elements in full implementation\n\n---\n\n### **packages/vue/src/index.ts**\n**Absolute Path:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue/src/index.ts`\n\n**Summary:** Public exports for the vue package:\n- Exports `VuePoint` plugin and `useAnnotationsStore` composable\n- Exports `VUEPOINT_ANNOTATIONS_KEY` Symbol\n- Exports `AnnotationsStore` type\n- Exports `useVueInspector` composable and its options type\n\n---\n\n## Architecture Summary\n\nThe annotation state management follows a **composable-based pattern**:\n\n1. **useAnnotationsStore()** (Vue) - Manages reactive annotation state without Pinia\n2. **Type definitions** (Core) - Defines all annotation, component, and webhook types\n3. **Plugin integration** - Provides store to entire app via Vue's inject/provide system\n4. **Formatting utilities** - Converts annotations to Markdown for AI agents\n5. **UI components** - Mount toolbar with annotation list and markers (stubs for Phase 2)\n\nAll paths are relative to `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/` and follow monorepo structure with separate `packages/vue` and `packages/core` directories."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a1ca6bc77a292af7f (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 39786\ntool_uses: 16\nduration_ms: 31612</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1f27ba3d-068a-4cf2-9738-8a97bb9a2ebc","uuid":"e39fb309-1001-4fe7-90d3-8ddffe2cde49","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Find files related to annotation state management in this monorepo. Look for:\n1. Any file named useAnnotations.ts or similar\n2. Any composable that manages annotation CRUD operations\n3. Check packages/vue/src/ and packages/core/src/ directories\n\nReport the file paths and a brief summary of what each contains. Be thorough - check both directories.","agentId":"a1ca6bc77a292af7f","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me provide you with a comprehensive report of all annotation state management files:\n\n## Annotation State Management Files Report\n\nI found **7 key files** related to annotation state management in the VuePoint monorepo:\n\n### **packages/vue/src/composables/useAnnotations.ts**\n**Absolute Path:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue/src/composables/useAnnotations.ts`\n\n**Summary:** The core annotation state management composable. This is the single source of truth for all annotations in the current session. It's a Vue 3 composition API function that manages reactive annotation state without using Pinia (intentionally isolated). Provides:\n- **State:** `annotations` (readonly), `pending` (computed filter)\n- **Reads:** `getById(id)`\n- **Writes (CRUD):** `create()`, `update()`, `acknowledge()`, `resolve()`, `dismiss()`, `remove()`, `clear()`\n- Exports `AnnotationsStore` type and `VUEPOINT_ANNOTATIONS_KEY` Symbol for inject/provide\n\n---\n\n### **packages/core/src/types.ts**\n**Absolute Path:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/core/src/types.ts`\n\n**Summary:** TypeScript type definitions for the annotation system:\n- `AnnotationStatus` type: 'pending' | 'acknowledged' | 'resolved' | 'dismissed'\n- `Annotation` interface: Full annotation object with selector, elementDescription, componentChain, feedback, expected/actual fields, timestamps, and status tracking fields\n- `AnnotationCreateInput` type: Input shape for creating annotations\n- `VueComponentInfo` interface: Component metadata (name, file path, line number, props)\n- `AnnotationRect` interface: Position/scroll data for annotation markers\n- `WebhookEvent` and `WebhookPayload` types for event notifications\n- `VuePointOptions` configuration type\n\n---\n\n### **packages/vue/src/plugin.ts**\n**Absolute Path:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue/src/plugin.ts`\n\n**Summary:** The main Vue 3 plugin that integrates annotation management:\n- Initializes `useAnnotationsStore()` composable\n- Provides annotation store to the entire app via `app.provide(VUEPOINT_ANNOTATIONS_KEY, annotationsStore)`\n- Creates an isolated Vue app instance for the VuePoint toolbar (prevents component chain pollution)\n- Registers keyboard shortcut (default: ctrl+shift+a) to toggle the toolbar\n- Guards against production builds (auto-disables if not in dev/staging)\n- Passes options and built component filters to toolbar\n\n---\n\n### **packages/core/src/output.ts**\n**Absolute Path:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/core/src/output.ts`\n\n**Summary:** Utilities for formatting annotations:\n- `formatAnnotation(ann, opts)`: Formats a single annotation as Markdown with selector, component chain, SFC path, Pinia stores, route, props, feedback, expected/actual\n- `formatAnnotationBatch(annotations, opts)`: Formats all pending annotations as a batch Markdown document\n- `generateId()`: Creates unique annotation IDs using timestamp + random string\n- `now()`: Returns current ISO timestamp\n\n---\n\n### **packages/vue/src/components/AnnotationPanel.vue**\n**Absolute Path:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue/src/components/AnnotationPanel.vue`\n\n**Summary:** UI component stub (Phase 2 - US-011). Currently a placeholder that:\n- Accepts `store: AnnotationsStore` prop\n- Emits `close` event\n- Will display scrollable list of all annotations in the full implementation\n\n---\n\n### **packages/vue/src/components/AnnotationMarker.vue**\n**Absolute Path:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue/src/components/AnnotationMarker.vue`\n\n**Summary:** UI component stub (Phase 2 - US-010). Currently a placeholder that:\n- Accepts `annotation: Annotation` and `index: number` props\n- Displays numbered badge for each annotation\n- Will be positioned overlay markers on annotated elements in full implementation\n\n---\n\n### **packages/vue/src/index.ts**\n**Absolute Path:** `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue/src/index.ts`\n\n**Summary:** Public exports for the vue package:\n- Exports `VuePoint` plugin and `useAnnotationsStore` composable\n- Exports `VUEPOINT_ANNOTATIONS_KEY` Symbol\n- Exports `AnnotationsStore` type\n- Exports `useVueInspector` composable and its options type\n\n---\n\n## Architecture Summary\n\nThe annotation state management follows a **composable-based pattern**:\n\n1. **useAnnotationsStore()** (Vue) - Manages reactive annotation state without Pinia\n2. **Type definitions** (Core) - Defines all annotation, component, and webhook types\n3. **Plugin integration** - Provides store to entire app via Vue's inject/provide system\n4. **Formatting utilities** - Converts annotations to Markdown for AI agents\n5. **UI components** - Mount toolbar with annotation list and markers (stubs for Phase 2)\n\nAll paths are relative to `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/` and follow monorepo structure with separate `packages/vue` and `packages/core` directories."}],"totalDurationMs":31612,"totalTokens":39786,"totalToolUseCount":16,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":308,"cache_read_input_tokens":38173,"output_tokens":1300,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":308,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
