{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_014S29t51bswzS53eXoSKwst","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"US-007 is complete. There are still stories with `passes: false` remaining (US-008 through US-038).\n\n`вҳ… Insight в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`\nThe `ReturnType<typeof useAnnotationsStore>` pattern used for `AnnotationsStore` is a powerful TypeScript technique вҖ” it means the type automatically stays in sync with the composable's return shape. When I added the `resolved` computed, consumers that use `AnnotationsStore` immediately gained access to it without any manual type updates. This \"inferred return type\" pattern is especially useful in Vue composables where the return object evolves frequently.\n`в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":322,"cache_read_input_tokens":65790,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":322},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1f27ba3d-068a-4cf2-9738-8a97bb9a2ebc","uuid":"f5388798-aa34-4d9b-b8f8-8a0ee178de6b"}
