{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01MSedJUkBKgCxUckRS7Ngin","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Typecheck passes. Let me verify all acceptance criteria against the existing code:\n\n`вҳ… Insight в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`\n**US-008 is already fully implemented** in the original source files. Here's what each AC maps to:\n\n1. **`app.use(VuePoint)` zero config** вҖ” `plugin.ts:24-25`: Plugin typed as `Plugin<VuePointOptions | undefined>`, options default to `{}`\n2. **`app.use(VuePoint, { ...options })` full options** вҖ” `plugin.ts:25`: accepts `VuePointOptions`\n3. **Production guard** вҖ” `plugin.ts:27-33`: checks `process.env.NODE_ENV !== 'production'` and `!import.meta.env?.PROD`\n4. **Isolated Vue app** вҖ” `plugin.ts:59-68`: `createToolbarApp()` creates a *separate* Vue app via `createApp()`, mounted on a new `<div id=\"__vuepoint-root\">`, so VuePoint components never appear in the host app's `__vueParentComponent` chain\n5. **Keyboard shortcut** вҖ” `plugin.ts:71-75` + `registerShortcut()`: parses `ctrl+shift+a` format, listens on `keydown`\n6. **Typecheck passes** вҖ” confirmed above\n`в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`\n\nAll acceptance criteria pass. Let me mark this story complete and commit."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6715,"cache_read_input_tokens":62379,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":6715},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"13cce48e-d1fa-4de0-9f52-e09ef01a7acd","uuid":"3ccbe248-dd0b-4322-9dc3-36d0bf506691"}
