- stub for US-010)\n- Annotation panel (scrollable list - stub for US-011)\n- Toolbar FAB with buttons:\n  - Main \"Annotate\" button (toggles annotation mode)\n  - Count badge (red circle with pending count)\n  - Copy-all button (copies Markdown to clipboard)\n\n**Styling:**\n- Uses `<style scoped>` with nested selector strategy\n- Dark theme: `#1a1a2e` background, `#e2e8f0` text\n- Highlight color: `#4f81bd` (blue)\n- Error color: `#ef4444` (red)\n- Transitions: `.vp-fade` (opacity), `.vp-slide` (transform)\n- Z-index: `2147483646` (highlight), `2147483647` (toolbar) - well above everything\n\n**Special Helper Function:**\n```ts\nhighlightStyle(el: Element): Record<string, string>\n// Computes CSS position styles from element's bounding rect + scroll offset\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. **AnnotationMarker.vue** (Stub - `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue/src/components/AnnotationMarker.vue`)\n\n**Status:** Minimal stub component\n\n```vue\n<script setup>\n// Props: annotation, index\n</script>\n\n<template>\n  <div data-vuepoint=\"true\" class=\"vp-marker\">\n    {{ index }}\n  </div>\n</template>\n```\n\n**Planned in US-010:**\n- Render numbered badge positioned absolutely over annotated elements\n- Display metadata on hover\n- Click to highlight related panel entry\n\n---\n\n### 3. **AnnotationPanel.vue** (Stub - `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue/src/components/AnnotationPanel.vue`)\n\n**Status:** Minimal stub component\n\n```vue\n<script setup>\n// Props: store (AnnotationsStore)\n// Emits: close\n</script>\n\n<template>\n  <div data-vuepoint=\"true\" class=\"vp-panel\">\n    <slot />\n  </div>\n</template>\n```\n\n**Planned in US-011:**\n- Scrollable list of all annotations\n- Status badges (pending/resolved/dismissed)\n- Action buttons for each annotation\n- Search/filter capabilities\n\n---\n\n### 4. **useVueInspector.ts** (Complete - `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue/src/composables/useVueInspector.ts`)\n\n**Purpose:** Walk Vue 3's internal component instance tree\n\n**Key Implementation:**\n- Reads `__vueParentComponent` property (attached by Vue 3 in dev builds)\n- This is the same property Vue DevTools uses\n- **Production graceful degradation:** Returns empty array in production builds (property stripped)\n\n**Main Function: `getComponentChain(el: Element): VueComponentInfo[]`**\n- Walks DOM upward to find nearest element with Vue instance\n- Traverses instance tree collecting component info\n- Returns array ordered: App вҶ’ Page вҶ’ ... вҶ’ LeafComponent\n- Filters components based on `filterSet` (PrimeVue internals, Vue builtins)\n\n**Component Name Resolution Priority:**\n1. `__name` (set by `<script setup>` compiler)\n2. `name` (from `defineComponent({ name: '...' })`)\n3. `__file` filename (fallback)\n\n**Secondary Function: `getComponentStores(chain, piniaInstance): string[]`**\n- Returns Pinia store IDs accessible to component\n- Reads from `pinia._s` (internal Map of stores)\n- Current: returns all active stores for leaf component\n- Phase 2: Enhanced to check actual component bindings\n\n**Helper Functions:**\n- `extractComponentInfo()` - Resolves name, file path, props\n- `filenameToName()` - Extracts PascalCase from SFC filename\n- `normalizePath()` - Converts absolute paths to project-relative\n\n---\n\n### 5. **useAnnotations.ts** (Complete - `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue/src/composables/useAnnotations.ts`)\n\n**Purpose:** Isolated annotation state management (NOT Pinia-based)\n\n**State Container:**\n```ts\nannotations: Ref<Annotation[]>\npending: Computed // filter by status='pending'\nresolved: Computed // filter by status='resolved'\nall: Readonly<Ref<Annotation[]>>\n```\n\n**Write Operations:**\n```ts\ncreate(input: AnnotationCreateInput): Annotation\n  // Generates ID, timestamps, returns new annotation\n\nupdate(id: string, patch: Partial<Annotation>): Annotation | null\n  // General patch + updatedAt timestamp\n\nacknowledge(id: string): Annotation | null\n  // status вҶ’ 'acknowledged', sets acknowledgedAt\n\nresolve(id: string, summary?: string, resolvedBy?: string): Annotation | null\n  // status вҶ’ 'resolved', sets resolvedAt, resolutionSummary\n\ndismiss(id: string, reason?: string): Annotation | null\n  // status вҶ’ 'dismissed', sets dismissReason\n\nremove(id: string): boolean\n  // Removes from array\n\nclear(): void\n  // Clears all annotations\n```\n\n**Read Operations:**\n```ts\ngetById(id: string): Annotation | undefined\n```\n\n**Exports:**\n- `VUEPOINT_ANNOTATIONS_KEY` - Symbol for provide/inject\n- Type: `AnnotationsStore` = return type of `useAnnotationsStore()`\n\n---\n\n### 6. **plugin.ts** (Complete - `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue/src/plugin.ts`)\n\n**Vue 3 Plugin Interface:**\n```ts\nconst VuePoint: Plugin<VuePointOptions | undefined> = {\n  install(app: App, options: VuePointOptions = {}) { ... }\n}\n```\n\n**Installation Steps:**\n\n1. **Production Guard:**\n   - Auto-disables in production (checks `process.env.NODE_ENV` or `import.meta.env.PROD`)\n   - Warnings if Vue 3 dev build not detected (`__VUE__` global)\n\n2. **Build Filter Set:**\n   - Calls `buildFilter(options.filterComponents)`\n   - Default: PrimeVue components + Vue builtins filtered\n   - Can pass custom array or `false` to disable all filtering\n\n3. **Create Annotation Store:**\n   - Calls `useAnnotationsStore()`\n   - Provides to app via `VUEPOINT_ANNOTATIONS_KEY` symbol\n   - Also provides options with `filterSet` via `VUEPOINT_OPTIONS_KEY`\n\n4. **Mount Toolbar Overlay:**\n   - Creates isolated Vue 3 app instance\n   - Mounts to `<div id=\"__vuepoint-root\" data-vuepoint=\"true\">`\n   - Passes `annotationsStore` and `options` as props\n   - Isolation prevents VuePoint from appearing in host app's component chain\n\n5. **Keyboard Shortcut Registration:**\n   - Default: `Ctrl+Shift+A`\n   - Parses shortcut string: `\"ctrl+shift+a\"` вҶ’ modifiers + key\n   - Dispatches `vuepoint:toggle` custom event on document\n   - Toolbar listens to this event\n\n6. **Console Logging:**\n   - Logs initialization with shortcut, MCP/API ports if enabled\n\n**Type Exports:**\n- `VUEPOINT_OPTIONS_KEY` symbol\n- `VUEPOINT_INSPECTOR_KEY` symbol\n\n---\n\n### 7. **types.ts** (Complete - `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/core/src/types.ts`)\n\n**Annotation Status Enum:**\n```ts\ntype AnnotationStatus = 'pending' | 'acknowledged' | 'resolved' | 'dismissed'\n```\n\n**Core Types:**\n\n**`VueComponentInfo`** - Single component in chain\n```ts\n{\n  name: string          // PascalCase component name\n  file?: string         // src/views/users/UserCard.vue\n  line?: number         // Best-effort from source maps\n  propKeys?: string[]   // Top-level prop names (no values)\n}\n```\n\n**`AnnotationRect`** - Bounding box info\n```ts\n{ x, y, width, height, scrollX, scrollY }\n```\n\n**`Annotation`** - Full annotation object\n```ts\n{\n  id: string\n  selector: string          // CSS selector path\n  elementDescription: string // Human-readable\n  componentChain: VueComponentInfo[]\n  piniaStores?: string[]\n  route?: string            // Current route path\n  feedback: string          // User input\n  expected?: string         // Structured field\n  actual?: string           // Structured field\n  screenshot?: string       // Base64 PNG (Phase 2)\n  status: AnnotationStatus\n  createdAt: string         // ISO timestamp\n  updatedAt: string\n  acknowledgedAt?: string\n  resolvedAt?: string\n  resolvedBy?: string\n  resolutionSummary?: string\n  dismissReason?: string\n}\n```\n\n**`AnnotationCreateInput`** - What's required to create\n```ts\nPick<Annotation, 'selector' | 'elementDescription' | 'componentChain' | 'feedback'>\n& Partial<Pick<Annotation, 'piniaStores' | 'route' | 'expected' | 'actual' | 'screenshot'>>\n```\n\n**Webhook Types:**\n- `WebhookEvent` enum: `'annotation.created'`, `'annotation.updated'`, `'annotation.acknowledged'`, `'annotation.resolved'`, `'annotation.dismissed'`, `'annotation.batch_copied'`, `'session.started'`, `'session.ended'`\n- `WebhookPayload` - Event + annotation + metadata\n- `WebhookConfig` - URL + secret + event filter\n\n**Plugin Config:**\n```ts\ninterface VuePointOptions {\n  enabled?: boolean\n  filterComponents?: string[] | false\n  shortcut?: string // default 'ctrl+shift+a'\n  pinia?: {\n    enabled: boolean\n    instance?: unknown\n  }\n  mcp?: {\n    enabled: boolean\n    port?: number\n    authToken?: string\n  }\n  api?: {\n    enabled: boolean\n    port?: number\n    authToken?: string\n    cors?: string[]\n  }\n  webhooks?: WebhookConfig[]\n  appMeta?: {\n    name?: string\n    version?: string\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Output Options:**\n```ts\ninterface MarkdownOutputOptions {\n  includeScreenshot?: boolean\n  includeProps?: boolean\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 8. **selector.ts** (Complete - `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/core/src/selector.ts`)\n\n**Function: `generateSelector(target: Element): string`**\n\n**Strategy (priority order):**\n1. Unique ID (skip auto-generated like `:r0:`)\n2. Unique `data-testid`, `data-cy`, `data-e2e`, `aria-label`, `name`, or `role` attribute\n3. Tag + classes (filters out Tailwind JIT hashes, CSS modules, >30 char classes, digit-starting)\n4. Nth-child fallback\n\n**Depth Limit:** MAX_DEPTH = 8 segments\n\n**Uniqueness Check:** `querySelectorAll()` returns length === 1\n\n**Returns:** CSS selector like `\".user-management-view .toolbar > .p-button:nth-child(2)\"`\n\n**Helper: `describeElement(el: Element): string`**\n\nFallback priority:\n1. Text content (80 chars max) вҶ’ `<tag> \"text\"`\n2. aria-label вҶ’ `<tag> [label]`\n3. Input type/placeholder вҶ’ `<input[type]> \"placeholder\"`\n4. Image alt вҶ’ `<img> \"alt\"`\n5. Tag name вҶ’ `<tag>`\n\n---\n\n### 9. **output.ts** (Complete - `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/core/src/output.ts`)\n\n**Function: `formatAnnotation(ann: Annotation, opts?: MarkdownOutputOptions): string`**\n\n**Output Format:**\n```markdown\n### Annotation [ann_id_last6]\n\n**Element:** `<div> \"text content\"`\n**Selector:** `.parent > .child:nth-child(2)`\n**Component:** `<App> вҶ’ <UserManagementView> вҶ’ <UserToolbar> вҶ’ <PButton>`\n**SFC Path:** `src/views/users/UserManagementView.vue`\n**Pinia Stores:** `userStore`, `appStore`\n**Route:** `/users/management`\n**Props:** `title`, `disabled`, `loading`\n\n**Feedback:** User's input text\n\n**Expected:** [optional structured field]\n**Actual:** [optional structured field]\n\n**Screenshot:** ![annotation](base64...)\n```\n\n**Function: `formatAnnotationBatch(annotations: Annotation[], opts?): string`**\n\n- Header: `## VuePoint Annotations`\n- Count: `> N pending annotation(s)`\n- Each annotation separated by `---`\n- Filters to pending annotations only\n\n**Helper Functions:**\n- `generateId()` вҶ’ `ann_${timestamp_base36}${random}` (unique)\n- `now()` вҶ’ `new Date().toISOString()`\n\n---\n\n### 10. **primevue-filter.ts** (Complete - `/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/core/src/primevue-filter.ts`)\n\n**PRIMEVUE_FILTER Array:** 31 component names\n- Layout: VirtualScroller, Portal, Teleport\n- Animation: Transition, VueBaseTransition\n- Icons: SpinnerIcon, CheckIcon, ChevronDownIcon, etc. (28 icon types)\n- Misc: FocusTrap, Ripple\n\n**VUE_BUILTINS Array:** 10 Vue internals\n- Transitions, KeepAlive, Suspense, Teleport\n- RouterView, RouterLink, Fragment, Comment, Text\n\n**Function: `buildFilter(option: string[] | false | undefined): Set<string>`**\n- `false` вҶ’ No filtering (empty Set)\n- `Array` вҶ’ VUE_BUILTINS + custom array\n- `undefined` вҶ’ VUE_BUILTINS + PRIMEVUE_FILTER (default)\n\n---\n\n### 11. **Index Exports** \n\n**`/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/core/src/index.ts`:**\n```ts\n// Types\nexport type {\n  AnnotationStatus, VueComponentInfo, AnnotationRect, Annotation,\n  AnnotationCreateInput, WebhookEvent, WebhookPayload,\n  WebhookConfig, VuePointOptions, MarkdownOutputOptions\n}\n\n// Functions\nexport { generateSelector, describeElement }\nexport { formatAnnotation, formatAnnotationBatch, generateId, now }\nexport { PRIMEVUE_FILTER, VUE_BUILTINS, buildFilter }\n```\n\n**`/Users/juergen/Downloads/VuePoint/packages/vue/src/index.ts`:**\n```ts\n// Plugin\nexport { VuePoint, default }\nexport { useAnnotationsStore, VUEPOINT_ANNOTATIONS_KEY }\nexport type { AnnotationsStore }\nexport { useVueInspector }\nexport type { UseVueInspectorOptions }\n```\n\n---\n\n## Summary: Architecture & Design Patterns\n\n**Isolation & Security:**\n- VuePoint DOM marked with `data-vuepoint=\"true\"` everywhere\n- Toolbar in isolated Vue 3 app instance (not in host app's provide/inject)\n- Annotation store never pollutes host app's Pinia\n- No Vue DevTools extension required\n\n**State Flow:**\n```\nDOM Click вҶ’ handleDocumentClick() \n  вҶ’ pendingElement = target\n  вҶ’ mode = 'panel' (show feedback modal)\n  вҶ’ submitAnnotation()\n  вҶ’ annotationsStore.create() (reactive)\n  вҶ’ VuePointToolbar re-renders (count badge, markers)\n```\n\n**Keyboard Handling:**\n1. User presses Ctrl+Shift+A вҶ’ keyboard listener in plugin\n2. Dispatches `vuepoint:toggle` custom event\n3. Toolbar listens вҶ’ toggles enterAnnotationMode/exitAnnotationMode\n4. In annotation mode: `e.preventDefault()` + `e.stopPropagation()` blocks all clicks\n\n**Component Hierarchy Resolution:**\n- Vue 3 internal: `__vueParentComponent` on DOM elements (dev builds only)\n- Walk DOM вҶ’ find instance вҶ’ traverse up instance tree\n- Collect filtered component names + SFC paths\n- Graceful degradation in production (empty array)\n\n**CSS Selector Generation:**\n- Smart heuristics prioritizing stable selectors\n- Filters out dynamic/generated classes\n- Stops at unique anchor points (IDs, data-testid)\n- Max 8 segments deep\n\n**Markdown Export:**\n- Single annotation: Readable card format\n- Batch: Pending-only list with separator lines\n- Greppable: component names, file paths, selectors are literal strings\n\n---\n\n## Current State for US-009\n\nвң… **Complete & Ready:**\n- VuePointToolbar.vue (full UI + click capture)\n- useVueInspector.ts (component hierarchy)\n- useAnnotations.ts (state management)\n- plugin.ts (Vue 3 integration)\n- Core types, selector, output, filters\n\nрҹҡ§ **Stubs for Future US:**\n- AnnotationMarker.vue (US-010: positioned badges)\n- AnnotationPanel.vue (US-011: scrollable list)\n\n**All code is production-ready for the click-to-annotate flow**"}],"totalDurationMs":76434,"totalTokens":61369,"totalToolUseCount":35,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":553,"cache_read_input_tokens":55953,"output_tokens":4858,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":553,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
