{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01U1GKVGyLL2s9hZ782xThNu","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`вҳ… Insight в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`\n**US-009 was largely pre-implemented** from the original 11 source files. The key fix was a subtle Vue 3 SFC gotcha: `highlightStyle()` was defined in a separate `<script>` block, which makes it a module export but NOT a template binding. In Vue 3, only `<script setup>` bindings are auto-exposed to templates. This wouldn't cause a TypeScript error (because `tsc --noEmit` with `.vue` shims doesn't check templates), but would fail at runtime with `highlightStyle is not a function`.\n`в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`\n\nUS-009 is complete. There are still stories with `passes: false` (US-010 through US-038), so more iterations are needed."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":237,"cache_read_input_tokens":84020,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":237},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d22e533d-f41a-4d26-96cc-a989c39cb512","uuid":"307f6242-af86-485e-a0f0-3d9699ff4a84"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":218885,"duration_api_ms":212354,"num_turns":20,"result":"`вҳ… Insight в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`\n**US-009 was largely pre-implemented** from the original 11 source files. The key fix was a subtle Vue 3 SFC gotcha: `highlightStyle()` was defined in a separate `<script>` block, which makes it a module export but NOT a template binding. In Vue 3, only `<script setup>` bindings are auto-exposed to templates. This wouldn't cause a TypeScript error (because `tsc --noEmit` with `.vue` shims doesn't check templates), but would fail at runtime with `highlightStyle is not a function`.\n`в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`\n\nUS-009 is complete. There are still stories with `passes: false` (US-010 through US-038), so more iterations are needed.","stop_reason":null,"session_id":"d22e533d-f41a-4d26-96cc-a989c39cb512","total_cost_usd":1.2822554000000002,"usage":{"input_tokens":19,"cache_creation_input_tokens":67308,"cache_read_input_tokens":1191552,"output_tokens":5972,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":67308,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":19,"outputTokens":5972,"cacheReadInputTokens":1191552,"cacheCreationInputTokens":67308,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":1.1658460000000002,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":52,"outputTokens":7334,"cacheReadInputTokens":425324,"cacheCreationInputTokens":29724,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.11640940000000002,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"31f77d5c-510