{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01MwYaTGrEhM73NioBp2KAwa","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`вҳ… Insight в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`\n- The AnnotationMarker uses a \"find by selector\" pattern вҖ” it doesn't store element references (which would break on re-renders), instead re-querying the DOM via `document.querySelector()`. This is more resilient to Vue's virtual DOM reconciliation.\n- Scroll event listeners use `capture: true` to catch scroll events from nested scrollable containers (e.g., a scrollable table inside the page), not just window-level scrolling.\n`в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`\n\n**US-010 complete.** The AnnotationMarker component now:\n- Renders positioned numbered badges at each annotation's target element\n- Tracks position on scroll/resize using RAF-debounced event listeners\n- Emits `select` on click to open the annotation panel\n- Colors badges by status: blue (pending), orange (acknowledged), green (resolved), gray (dismissed)\n\nThere are still stories with `passes: false` remaining (US-011 is the next priority-1 story)."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":203,"cache_read_input_tokens":75807,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":203},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"687ab712-1fb4-4555-8189-5ddee3c408c3","uuid":"91554a5f-6b35-441c-a6fc-5fdc848276ae"}
